                        <interp inst="t18561027-name-682" type="given" value="JOHN JAMES"></interp>JOHN JAMES THOMASON</persName>
                  </hi>. I live at Deptford. I was standing outside the prosecutor's door—I saw the prisoner run out of the shop—he had his hand in his pocket—I ran after him—I did not catch him—I am sure he is the person.</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="185610270164"></xptr>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> They accused me the next morning; I went down with the constable,. and the prosecutor said I was the person; I was at Woolwich all the time.</p>
