                  </hi>. (<hi rend="italic">policeman, R</hi> 82). Nothing was found on him—he had a blue jacket on when he committed the robbery—the next morning he was dressed the same as he is now, in a blue smock—I asked him what he had done with his jacket—he said he had sold it—I have since found the jacket where he left it on the afternoon of this robbery.</p>
